Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.81,0:00:04.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rhythm of the wind clears reasoning,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Always confirming that vital clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jewel robbers are on the loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.78,0:00:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This incident can't delay it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:12.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recognizing that single truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:16.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After finding the murderer of Itakura-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:50.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I followed up on my lead to the Black Organization\Nthanks to Professor Agasa, which lead us to...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:52.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Itakura-san's cottage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:54.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:03.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vodka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:08.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:14.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means. they must have found out tha\Ntwe failed to open their e-mail at this cabin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:15.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you're in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:28.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You better pick up the phone, Itakura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:29.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:41.01,Title,,0,0,0,,Contact With the Black Organization\N(Pursuit Chapter){Title}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Contact With the Black Organization, Pursuit Chapter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:48.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you're in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You better pick up the phone. Itakura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:03:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have no other choice, we'll have to go out into the\Nblizzard through the backdoor, despite the danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't find the phone in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:09.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess the lines got disconnected due to the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The power went out before I could check my mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:21.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have tried to open the mail out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:26.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a second, why'd you open it at a \Nplace where a blackout could happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:31.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blackouts happen often in this weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:35.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the only place I can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:39.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:45.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a question, how did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:47.33,Signs,,0,0,0,,Turn on the lights!{Sign}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:50.37,Signs,,0,0,0,,Turn on the lights!{Sign}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:51.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's actions are predictable to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:56.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope you all haven't been watching my cottage as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We weren't, don't worry'.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:00.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope you finished that in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:03.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope you finished that in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The computer system program we hired you to complete by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:09.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I barely did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:13.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is someone else there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, answer me. What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:17.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:23.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The noise was made by the wind blowing against the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:27.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I heard it was snowing heavily there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:30.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't use my computer at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:33.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you just tell me over the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When and where I'll be meeting you to hand over the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:42.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, because I won't repeat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know the Kenbashi station that's under construction?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:49.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a station that will become a part of the Touto line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow at midnight, meet me at the\Nunderground coin locker #0032.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:01.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to bring the computer program.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't, tomorrow isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:06.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be staying at the hospital then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:14.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you know, I have heart issues...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:21.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be you're trying to buy time to finish the program?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's already finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The program is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then when would be good?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be released from the hospital in three or four days...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, about five days from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:37.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fool, we can't wait that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just cancel your appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It took me a long time to get an appointment\Nwith this renowned heart surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:45.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't cancel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:51.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only time I can give it to you before my appointment\Nis today, but the site workers will be there in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:54.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't wont them around, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:59.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then at 4:00. At 4:00, bring to the place I just mentioned...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The computer program.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 4:00?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From Gunma to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:11.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it? It shouldn't be a problem if the programs are done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:15.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got it. I'll meet you in four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I want you to assure me of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:24.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Promise me this isn't a trick so you can ambush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could take it by force,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:31.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then you would lose all means of accessing the disk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like they said, you are an old bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:38.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, in four hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be at Kenbashi Station, Locker #0032. Don't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:45.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, I've get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing? You're nor thinking of dancing\Nto their tune and taking the disk right to them, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:01.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not dancing to their tune.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I manipulated the conversation to\Nhave the meeting moved to 4:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:09.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By pretending I was desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:16.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The news of Itakura-san's murder should\Nbe on the news this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:20.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this meeting was cancelled, I wouldnli be able to trap them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:27.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that the jewel robbers are still on the run.{Top}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:27.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Luckily, no station has aired the news about his death yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:30.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Then, your plan was to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:30.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:37.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I planned to reply to their mail to move\Nthe meeting time up anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's remove our fingerprints from everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And get in your Beetle and quickly get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:47.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-Get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you said they could be watching this cottage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:57.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if they see us get into the car out front?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:58.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:02.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Vodka or his associates were around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They would have known that the lack\Nof power for the computer was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:13.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, that's why told me ta turn an the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:14.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's likely that they aren't even near the cottage,\Nor at least in view of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:26.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They only found this place because that mail has a program\Nthat traces where it was failed to be opened from,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:32.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Giving them exactly where that computer system is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we can get some of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:40.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this disk contains a special program that\Ncould be misused to commit crimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:46.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially if they're dangerous\Ncrimes, we'll have them arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:50.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we tell the police. they can go stake out the station,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:54.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so then they'll walk right into our trap and get arrested!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:55.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, it's not working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:04.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This disk requires a password as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:10.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just like the one Itakura-san and them agreed on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's at least make a copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no use, there's a copy-guard on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:20.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have nothing to tell the police now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:24.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't those guys always carry guns?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we report to the police that they're\Nselling illegal weapons, they'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We really don't know how many officers they would send.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they only sent a few, they could be seriously injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:42.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we reality want the police to come, we'll have to present: them\Nwith evidence of how dangerous this Organization is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We must never face them unless we're completely prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's frustrating. We know where they are and Still can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there's something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:01.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's rather dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:05.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, do you mean to meet them in person?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Profes.sor, tell me it isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:12.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:17.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a flat as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:23.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll have to ask a gas station neor by to bring us a spore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:29.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that alright? That'll take forever, especially at this hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we can just wait in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:36.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not that, I won't make The meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:41.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably God's way of telling you\Nnot to do such dangerous things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A car!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:10:59.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:03.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing, just some tire trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:07.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were heading to Tokyo, can you give us a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo, how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not, we're headed that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Old man, are you familiar with these roods?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Old man. take the passenger seat. Kid, you're in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:24.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:35.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, lady, I saw you sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:38.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's alright, I was only resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:50.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome! This car is a cool import!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, is This yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:58.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I'm thinking of trading it in for something better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you must be rich, this is an expensive car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:05.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He may not look it, but he's the heir to a big company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've gotta be careful on snowy roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, just drive carefully and safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I just heard something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? I didn't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:45.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just our luggage in the trunk, nothing to worry over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:48.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten? I hate cigarettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:59.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokyo is on the left ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:00.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it stopped snowing, we should make it by 3:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:13.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why were in you in Gunma? Were\Nyou skiing with your grandson?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:15.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry, I knew we shouldn't have taken a snowy road.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:48.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:50.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:51.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Shiny Logo}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:11.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you mind? How many honks is that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:15.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I said, I'm not good on snowy roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:20.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's right, mister,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:24.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have to drive carefully since this\Ncar is this tired before its inspection.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This car is coming up for inspection soon, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:30.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:35.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:40.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The number on The outside of the windshield is a "2".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that sticker tell you by it's color and\N number when the car should be inspected?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:56.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This year's color is obvious so it mean\Nit should be checked in February.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:59.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got a reminder in the mail earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, boy, when did you see the sticker? It's covered by snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:12.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, I saw it when a car would poss us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The number will show through when it's lit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:31.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it was a 2 from the back, but I bet it's really a 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's strange, you got a reminder in the mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:40.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:47.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I told you earlier, he's the heir to a large company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:54.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone else takes care of things like inspections for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:59.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should have taken that left to get to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:07.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, boy, stop bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:11.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, he's a curious one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:14.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What have you been listening to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:28.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this? It's the news on the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:30.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,News?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:33.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep, there's been lots of news.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:38.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reports about the recovering economy,\Nabout the baseball game...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And also about those jewelry store robbers on the run.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:46.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, boy, you really like the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:47.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:52.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then? Did they catch the jewel robbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:53.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:56.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're still running about Gunma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:59.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it won't be too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because look, there's a police checkpoint ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:14.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your license, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me what you're doing out so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:23.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, see..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:25.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Yamamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:28.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:35.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Officer Yamamura, this checkpoint\Nis to catch the jewel robbers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three robbers were involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They switched out of the getaway car from the jewel heist,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:49.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because we found that car in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, we don't think those three have gotten\Nfar, because one of them is injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:17:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:00.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:05.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bullet I fired as a warning shot struck one of them in the thigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I almost caught those three jewel robbers on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:15.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I raised my gun and it was like the movies...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Stop! Put your hands up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:18.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If those criminals try to mess with me, I'll shoot them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:27.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:28.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, I can arrest all of the criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:41.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We think the robbers had a car hidden in the forest to escape in,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or maybe that they hijacked one that came by.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:49.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't see anything like that did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:51.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,People riding in someone else's car?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you're talking about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:02.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of my tires went flat on my car back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These people were kind enough to give us a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agasa-san, then your car is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:18.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My dealer told me they would send someone\Nup for it later, so I left the key in it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But is that really a good thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those criminals could be driving your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's definitely a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:34.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, shouldn't you be trying to catch\Nthat car rather than talking to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a yellow Beetle, can't miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:39.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've heard your voices before...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:44.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're imagining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:47.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, can we go. Officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you take your jacket off your lap?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you suspecting us!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:01.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look. I'm not shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:03.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:05.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drive safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes? This is Agasa's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guhma police?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agasa-san said the dealer would come get it in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we cant just leave it here, since the\Njewel robbers could take it anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:41.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we've got a wrecker here to toke it to the police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please tell him to call the department whenever he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:48.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:50.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:51.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is he doing out so late near Gunma?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:03.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be Kudo-kun, trying to get him involved in a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:09.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Going out at this hour to investigate...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:12.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's so fun about being a detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The spare Homing Glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:40.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right, the meeting's been moved up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an hour from now, 4:00, at the coin lockers of\Nthe Kenbashi station that's under construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:50.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let my partner Gin know about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.62,0:22:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make sure you have enough armed men around.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This guy may have called the cops, trying to trick us...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll eliminate him at Kenbashi station when the deal's done.
